title: NFL Draft: Most Interesting Teams Pt. 2, Top 10 LB Prospects (Football 4/15)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson and Sean Wagner-McGough to continue their discussion on the 'most interesting' teams in the NFL Draft, with a focus on the Vikings (3:00) and Colts (11:15). What does Minnesota do with the pick they acquired for Stefon Diggs? Could Indy really target a quarterback as an eventual Philip Rivers replacement? Next, draft expert Emory Hunt joins the pod to analyze his Top 10 linebackers in the 2020 Draft (18:15)
